Package: shinyblocks
Title: Composable Modern UI Blocks for Shiny
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Niels", "van der Velden", , "n.s.j.vandervelden@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides composable Shiny dashboard components inspired by
    shadcn/ui, with R-first helpers, bundled assets, and accessible
    defaults. End users do not need Node, Tailwind, or React.
